ch.epfl.lasec.evoting
Class VotingObject

java.lang.Object
  ch.epfl.lasec.evoting.VotingObject

public abstract class VotingObject
extends java.lang.Object

abstract class representing an object submitted to a vote. The object has a subject and a type. The type is either election or question.

Author:
Sebastien Duc
